<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SFDPH SUS New Admit Workflow Guides</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy:    #1B2A4A;
    --teal:    #1E8A8A;
    --teal-lt: #E6F5F5;
    --amber:   #F5A623;
    --amber-lt:#FEF6E4;
    --coral:   #D94F45;
    --coral-lt:#FDECEA;
    --green:   #2E7D5E;
    --green-lt:#E6F4EE;
    --purple:  #6D28D9;
    --purple-lt:#F5F3FF;
    --silver:  #F0F4F8;
    --mid:     #8898AA;
    --border:  #D0DBE8;
    --text:    #1A2535;
    --text-sm: #4A5568;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    background: #E8EDF4;
    color: var(--text);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── Site Header ── */
  .site-header {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 14px 28px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
  }
  .logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .logo-icon {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; background: var(--teal); border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700; color: white; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: -.5px;
  }
  .site-header h1 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: white; }
  .site-header .sub { font-size: 10.5px; color: #8BAFD4; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .dept-badge {
    background: var(--teal); color: white;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: .5px; text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── Tab Bar ── */
  .tab-bar {
    background: var(--navy);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
    display: flex; overflow-x: auto; padding: 0 12px; gap: 2px;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  .tab-bar::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .tab-btn {
    background: transparent; border: none; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    color: #8BAFD4; font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11.5px; font-weight: 500; padding: 10px 14px;
    cursor: pointer; white-space: nowrap; transition: color .15s, border-color .15s;
  }
  .tab-btn:hover { color: white; }
  .tab-btn.active { color: var(--amber); border-bottom-color: var(--amber); }

  /* ── Pages ── */
  .page { display: none; padding: 24px 20px 48px; max-width: 1140px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .page.active { display: block; }

  /* ── Guide card ── */
  .guide-card {
    background: white; border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .guide-header {
    background: var(--navy); padding: 16px 22px;
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  }
  .guide-num {
    width: 34px; height: 34px; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--teal); border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: white; margin-top: 1px;
  }
  .guide-header-text h2 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: white; line-height: 1.3; }
  .guide-header-text .purpose { font-size: 11px; color: #8BAFD4; margin-top: 3px; line-height: 1.45; }
  .who-tag {
    margin-left: auto; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); color: #A8C8E8;
    font-size: 10px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 12px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; white-space: nowrap; align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .guide-body { padding: 20px 22px; }

  /* ── Flow ── */
  .flow { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .flow-step { display: flex; gap: 0; position: relative; }
  .step-connector { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; width: 36px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .step-dot {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--navy); color: white;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; z-index: 1;
  }
  .step-dot.teal   { background: var(--teal); }
  .step-dot.amber  { background: var(--amber); color: var(--navy); }
  .step-dot.coral  { background: var(--coral); }
  .step-dot.green  { background: var(--green); }
  .step-dot.purple { background: var(--purple); }
  .step-line { width: 2px; background: var(--border); flex: 1; min-height: 14px; }
  .step-line.last { display: none; }
  .step-content { flex: 1; padding: 0 0 20px 10px; }
  .step-phase {
    font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: .7px; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .step-title { font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .step-desc  { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.58; }

  /* ── Sub-steps (indented checklist style) ── */
  .sub-steps { margin-top: 8px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .sub-step {
    display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .sub-bullet {
    width: 16px; height: 16px; border-radius: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;
    background: var(--silver); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 8px; color: var(--mid); font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* ── Field pills ── */
  .fields { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; margin-top: 7px; }
  .field {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10.5px;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid; white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .field.blue   { background: #EEF4FF; color: #1D4ED8; border-color: #BFDBFE; }
  .field.teal   { background: var(--teal-lt); color: #0F766E; border-color: #99D6D6; }
  .field.amber  { background: var(--amber-lt); color: #92400E; border-color: #FCD34D; }
  .field.coral  { background: var(--coral-lt); color: var(--coral); border-color: #FECACA; }
  .field.green  { background: var(--green-lt); color: var(--green); border-color: #6EE7B7; }
  .field.gray   { background: var(--silver); color: var(--text-sm); border-color: var(--border); }
  .field.purple { background: var(--purple-lt); color: var(--purple); border-color: #C4B5FD; }

  /* ── Callouts ── */
  .callout {
    border-radius: 7px; padding: 9px 12px;
    font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.52; margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .callout.stop  { background: var(--coral-lt); border-left: 3px solid var(--coral); color: #7F1D1D; }
  .callout.warn  { background: var(--amber-lt); border-left: 3px solid var(--amber); color: #78350F; }
  .callout.info  { background: var(--teal-lt);  border-left: 3px solid var(--teal);  color: #134E4A; }
  .callout.ok    { background: var(--green-lt); border-left: 3px solid var(--green); color: #14532D; }
  .callout.role  { background: #F5F3FF; border-left: 3px solid var(--purple); color: #4C1D95; }
  .callout-label { font-weight: 700; font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .6px; margin-bottom: 3px; }

  /* ── Breadcrumb ── */
  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--mid);
    background: var(--silver); padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 5px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 7px;
  }
  .breadcrumb .crumb { color: var(--navy); font-weight: 600; }
  .breadcrumb .sep   { color: var(--border); }

  /* ── Epic mock buttons ── */
  .epic-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10.5px; font-weight: 500;
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid;
  }
  .epic-btn.primary { background: #0057B8; color: white; border-color: #0047A0; }
  .epic-btn.success { background: #1A7A4A; color: white; border-color: #155D39; }
  .epic-btn.warning { background: var(--amber); color: var(--navy); border-color: #D4920F; }
  .epic-btn.danger  { background: var(--coral); color: white; border-color: #B83D35; }
  .epic-btn.gray    { background: #6B7280; color: white; border-color: #4B5563; }

  /* ── Section divider ── */
  .section-divider {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin: 16px 0 13px;
  }
  .section-divider span {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .8px;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mid); white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .section-divider hr { flex: 1; border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }

  /* ── Phase progress strip ── */
  .phase-strip {
    display: flex; gap: 0; margin-bottom: 18px;
    border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .phase-item {
    flex: 1; padding: 8px 6px; text-align: center;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .3px;
    position: relative; line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .phase-item::after {
    content: '▶'; position: absolute; right: -6px; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%); font-size: 9px; z-index: 1; color: white;
  }
  .phase-item:last-child::after { display: none; }
  .ph1 { background: #1B2A4A; color: white; }
  .ph2 { background: #1E6B8A; color: white; }
  .ph3 { background: var(--teal); color: white; }
  .ph4 { background: var(--green); color: white; }
  .ph5 { background: var(--amber); color: var(--navy); }
  .ph6 { background: var(--coral); color: white; }
  .ph-done { background: #6B7280; color: white; }
  .ph-active { background: var(--teal); color: white; }

  /* ── Two / Three col ── */
  .two-col   { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; }
  .three-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .two-col, .three-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  /* ── Mini card ── */
  .mini-card {
    border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 11px 13px; background: var(--silver);
  }
  .mini-card h4 { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .mini-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .mini-card ul li {
    font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.55;
    padding: 2px 0 2px 14px; position: relative;
  }
  .mini-card ul li::before { content: '›'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--teal); font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── Role badge ── */
  .role-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px;
    padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid;
  }
  .role-badge.lpha   { background: var(--purple-lt); color: var(--purple); border-color: #C4B5FD; }
  .role-badge.aod    { background: var(--teal-lt); color: var(--teal); border-color: #99D6D6; }
  .role-badge.admin  { background: var(--amber-lt); color: #92400E; border-color: #FCD34D; }
  .role-badge.both   { background: var(--silver); color: var(--text-sm); border-color: var(--border); }

  /* ── Flowsheet grid (tab map) ── */
  .tab-map { border: 2px solid var(--navy); border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
  .tab-map-header { background: var(--navy); display: flex; overflow-x: auto; }
  .tab-map-tab {
    padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500;
    color: #8BAFD4; border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .tab-map-tab.active-tab { background: var(--teal); color: white; font-weight: 600; }
  .tab-map-body { background: white; padding: 16px; }
  .fs-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 8px; }
  @media (max-width: 600px) { .fs-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
  .fs-item {
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 10px; background: var(--silver);
  }
  .fs-item.hi  { border-color: var(--amber); background: var(--amber-lt); }
  .fs-item.tl  { border-color: var(--teal);  background: var(--teal-lt); }
  .fs-item.pu  { border-color: var(--purple); background: var(--purple-lt); }
  .fi-lbl { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .6px; color: var(--mid); margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .fi-nm  { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--navy); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3; }
  .fi-ds  { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--text-sm); margin-top: 3px; line-height: 1.4; }

  /* ── Consent comparison ── */
  .compare-card { border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid; overflow: hidden; }
  .compare-card.plan    { border-color: var(--teal); }
  .compare-card.summary { border-color: var(--amber); }
  .compare-header { padding: 11px 15px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; }
  .compare-card.plan    .compare-header { background: var(--teal); color: white; }
  .compare-card.summary .compare-header { background: var(--amber); color: var(--navy); }
  .compare-body { padding: 13px 15px; }
  .compare-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .compare-label { font-weight: 600; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: .5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--mid); width: 88px; flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 1px; }
  .compare-val { color: var(--text-sm); flex: 1; }

  /* ── ASAM table ── */
  .dim-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 11.5px; }
  .dim-table th { background: var(--navy); color: white; font-weight: 600; padding: 7px 10px; text-align: left; font-size: 10.5px; }
  .dim-table td { padding: 7px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.45; }
  .dim-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: var(--silver); }
  .dim-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .dim-num { font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--teal); }

  /* ── footnote ── */
  .footnote { font-size: 10px; color: var(--mid); margin-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 10px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ── write-down box ── */
  .write-down {
    border: 2px dashed var(--amber); border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px;
    background: var(--amber-lt); margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .write-down-label { font-size: 9.5px; font-weight: 700; color: #92400E; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .6px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .write-down-row { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .write-down-field {
    flex: 1; min-width: 140px;
    background: white; border: 1px solid #FCD34D; border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 8px 10px;
  }
  .wdf-label { font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; color: #92400E; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .wdf-line { height: 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid #FCD34D; }

  @media print {
    body { background: white; }
    .tab-bar, .site-header { display: none; }
    .page { display: block !important; page-break-after: always; padding: 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="site-header">
  <div class="logo">
    <div class="logo-icon">Rx</div>
    <div>
      <div class="sub">San Francisco DPH · BHS</div>
      <h1>SUS New Admit Workflow Guides</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <span class="dept-badge">Substance Use Services</span>
</header>

<nav class="tab-bar">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="show('w1',this)">① Residential Admission &amp; Consents</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show('w2',this)">② Initial Clinical Assessment</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show('w3',this)">③ Auth Linkage, REF283 &amp; Bed Days</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show('w4',this)">④ Consent Workflow (Digital)</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show('w5',this)">⑤ Assessment Tab Map</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show('w6',this)">⑥ Reauthorization</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show('w7',this)">⑦ Discharge Workflow</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="show('w8',this)">⑧ Plan vs. Summary</button>
</nav>


<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- WORKFLOW 1 — Residential Admission & Consent Verification  -->
<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="w1" class="page active">
  <div class="guide-card">
    <div class="guide-header">
      <div class="guide-num">1</div>
      <div class="guide-header-text">
        <h2>Residential Admission &amp; Consent Verification</h2>
        <div class="purpose">Formally admit the member and verify legal compliance before clinical documentation begins</div>
      </div>
      <span class="who-tag">Admin or Clinical Staff</span>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-body">

      <div class="callout stop" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
        <div class="callout-label">🛑 Context Requirement</div>
        You <strong>must</strong> be logged into a department whose name ends in <strong>"RESIDENTIAL"</strong>. Outpatient departments do not support the inpatient admission workflow. Verify your department label in the Epic toolbar before proceeding.
      </div>

      <div class="flow">

        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="step-connector"><div class="step-dot teal">1</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-phase">System Access</div>
            <div class="step-title">Log In &amp; Verify Department Context</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Launch <strong>PRD Hyperspace</strong> via the Citrix Gateway. Before doing anything else, confirm the department shown in your Epic toolbar ends in "RESIDENTIAL." If it does not, switch departments now.</div>
            <div class="fields">
              <span class="field coral">Department must end in "RESIDENTIAL" ✱</span>
              <span class="field gray">PRD Hyperspace via Citrix Gateway</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="step-connector"><div class="step-dot teal">2</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-phase">Navigation</div>
            <div class="step-title">Search Patient Station → New Admission</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Navigate to <strong>Patient Station</strong> — do not use Patient Lookup, which is for outpatient context. Search for the member and select <span class="epic-btn primary">New Admission</span>.</div>
            <div class="callout warn">
              <div class="callout-label">⚠ Do Not Use Patient Lookup</div>
              Patient Lookup will not surface the inpatient admission workflow. Always start from Patient Station for residential admits.
            </div>
            <div class="breadcrumb">
              <span class="crumb">Patient Station</span><span class="sep">›</span>
              <span class="crumb">Search Member</span><span class="sep">›</span>
              <span class="crumb">New Admission</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="step-connector"><div class="step-dot teal">3</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-phase">Data Entry</div>
            <div class="step-title">Complete All Admission Fields</div>
            <div class="step-desc">Fill every required field in the Admission Navigator. Missing any field will prevent the Admit button from activating.</div>
            <div class="sub-steps">
              <div class="sub-step"><div class="sub-bullet">a</div><div>Enter <strong>Expected Date</strong>, <strong>Unit</strong>, and <strong>Admitting Provider</strong></div></div>
              <div class="sub-step"><div class="sub-bullet" style="background:var(--coral-lt);border-color:var(--coral);color:var(--coral);">b</div><div>Set <strong>Patient Class</strong> to <span class="field amber" style="font-size:10px;">SUS Res</span> — wrong class causes downstream billing and reporting errors</div></div>
              <div class="sub-step"><div class="sub-bullet">c</div><div>Open the <strong>Destination</strong> tab → assign a specific <strong>Room</strong> and <strong>Bed</strong></div></div>
              <div class="sub-step"><div class="sub-bullet">d</div><div>Review the administrative <strong>Checklist</strong> for any missing data → click <span class="epic-btn success">Admit</span></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="callout stop">
              <div class="callout-label">🛑 Hard Stop — Patient Class</div>
              Patient Class <strong>must</strong> be set to <strong>"SUS Res"</strong>. Any other class will route the encounter incorrectly and affect authorization eligibility.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="step-connector"><div class="step-dot green">4</div><div class="step-line last"></div></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-phase">Compliance — Consent Verification</div>
            <div class="step-title">Chart Review → BHS SnapShot → Verify Consents</div>
            <div class="step-desc">After the admission is created, navigate to <strong>Chart Review &gt; BHS SnapShot</strong> and verify all three required consent forms are present and current.</div>
            <div class="breadcrumb">
              <span class="crumb">Chart Review</span><span class="sep">›</span>
              <span class="crumb">BHS SnapShot</span><span class="sep">›</span>
              <span class="crumb">Consent Status</span>
            </div>
            <div class="three-col" style="margin-top:10px;">
              <div style="border:1px solid var(--teal);border-radius:8px;padding:10px;background:var(--teal-lt);">
