            <div class="step-desc">Open the <strong>Patient Workqueue (WQF)</strong>. Locate the member in the <em>HS Res Auth/Cert</em> queue for your program. Double-click their row. On the Update Admission screen, click <span class="epic-btn gray">More ▾</span> → <strong>Auth/Cert Linkage</strong>.</div>
