          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-phase">Read Auth Details — Write These Down</div>
            <div class="step-title">Double-Click REF283 Entry → Open Questionnaire</div>
            <div class="step-desc">In the Auth/Certs list, find the row where the <strong>Orders</strong> column shows <em>REF283</em>. Double-click it. Click <strong>Questionnaire</strong> in the left sidebar and manually record both values before clicking Cancel.</div>
            <div class="write-down">
              <div class="write-down-label">✏ Write These Down Before Clicking Cancel</div>
              <div class="write-down-row">
                <div class="write-down-field">
                  <div class="wdf-label">Level of Care</div>
                  <div class="wdf-line"></div>
                  <div style="font-size:9.5px;color:#92400E;margin-top:3px;">e.g. BHS SUS 3.1</div>
                </div>
                <div class="write-down-field">
