              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="callout warn" style="margin-top:8px;">
              <div class="callout-label">⚠ Important Sequence</div>
              Click <strong>Cancel</strong> (not Close/Save) after noting the values. Then reopen the Auth/Cert record by double-clicking it again before proceeding to Bed Days.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- STEP 7 — Bed Days -->
        <div class="flow-step">
          <div class="step-connector"><div class="step-dot teal">7</div><div class="step-line"></div></div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-phase">Set Initial Bed Days</div>
            <div class="step-title">Bed Days Tab → + Add Entry</div>
            <div class="step-desc">In the reopened Auth/Cert Entry, click <strong>Bed Days</strong> in the left sidebar. Click <span class="epic-btn primary">+ Add Entry</span> and complete all four fields using the values recorded in Step 6.</div>
            <div style="border:1px solid var(--teal);border-radius:8px;padding:11px 14px;background:var(--teal-lt);margin-top:8px;">
              <div style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--teal);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;margin-bottom:8px;">Bed Day Entry — Required Fields</div>
              <div class="fields">
